Titolo: Golden Axe: Beast Rider

Anno: 2008

Descrizione: Golden Axe: Beast Rider is an action-adventure hack and slash video game for the Xbox 360 and PlayStation 3, published by Sega and developed by Secret Level. It is the first 3D entry in the Golden Axe franchise. The game was released in North America on October 14, 2008, in Europe on October 17, and in Australia on October 23.

Genere: Action-adventure 

Valutazione: 44
